%% Diagram: Diagram 2
%% Type: flowchart
flowchart LR
    subgraph SaleTime["During Sale"]
        WR[Waiting Room] --> RL[Rate Limiter]
        RL --> INV[Inventory Check<br/>Redis Counter]
        INV --> |count > 0| CHECKOUT[Checkout]
        INV --> |count = 0| SOLD[Sold Out]
        CHECKOUT --> DEC[Atomic Decrement]
    end
